    "asOf": "2019-07-31",
    "date": "2019-09-09T16:53:54Z",
    "text": "Addressing Teacher Shortages Act of 2019\n\nThis bill directs the Department of Education (ED) to establish an Addressing Teacher Shortages Program. Through this program, ED shall award grants for local education agencies\u00a0to address teacher shortage challenges.\n\nSpecifically, grant funds\u00a0may be used to establish or expand\n\n teaching residency programs, teacher mentor programs, specified recruitment and training programs, and other evidence-based strategies to increase teacher retention and support teachers."
